data.description:
Price Reduced To Sell!
This house design is unique with 10' ceiling as you walk in. 9' Flat on the first floor. Two patios with 3 accesses to them. Connected with concrete walk way. Large Laundry room with storage and hobby working area.  Rear load stairway offers semi privacy to other parts of the house. 
Upstairs bedrooms have built in closets with adjustable shelves and rods for custom designs. Large backyard makes a great home for kids. 

Neighborhood Description

Mostly new construction over the last 15 years.
